      "comment": "HARA'S GHOST (5) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 3.5 lengths (28.85) at this track. Looks the one to beat. PINK CAR (1) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when third (29.03) at this track in a Grade 5. Well placed here and can atone this time. LEMON SLICE (8) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Ashy Bear (29.08) in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Expecting another good run. BIG EARS REGRET (2) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
